Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓你們在地獄為反抗過我的事而後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.81,0:00:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要後悔的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還垂死掙扎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是不是垂死掙扎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就親身試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不能再支配我的靈魂了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧  德魯克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種程度的話  會很無聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  蘇伊露
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是妖精族的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看著我們吧  阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防禦水晶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉比塔斯的放出量越來越多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥的徵兆越來越強了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  不這樣怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈正加護於我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:06:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在地獄裡嘗到的痛苦和屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸使不上勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是古拉比塔斯的力量變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  明明大鍋就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絡繹不絕地出現中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絡繹不絕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我是不幸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說這個的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:06:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多的黑騎士竟被兩個人幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你們要高興還早得很
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我命令你們這些被創造的扭曲生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還又是一大群啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:07:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發牢騷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在進這座塔的時候就應該做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會發牢騷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到最後  我絕對不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我們要勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人  您要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是想用神聖魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開  奧伽姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓  決戰之時還等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事到時候再想就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這裡就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份痛苦正是那位大人的慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你復活的傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…在什麼地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見那位大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  讓我實現你的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過等我先拿下你的小命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:10:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底不過一個活人  是贏不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就體會著自己的無力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著重要的哥哥嚥下最後一口氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得憑你那樣的防禦魔法能抵擋得了它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你們兩個一起貫穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是空間轉移…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…被這樣…的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事  你有沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:14.83,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給予我力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多的…更多的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光芒變得更強了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我充滿了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想中的世界  阿努文的門終於打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上的那些傢伙重振旗鼓後會一口氣投下奧貝里斯克的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後那個怪物會出現在充滿古拉比塔斯的地上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露卡迪斯…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.45,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露卡迪斯：神之戰車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個麻煩的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼辦法讓它弱化就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓梅露卡迪斯的力量弱化？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能做到還是個未知數
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個方法就在某個詩篇集中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你得到了神聖百詩篇集？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…光是那樣還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩篇集中的咒歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能讓梅露卡迪斯弱化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它也被稱為「力量的咒文」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能詠唱的人卻不多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有條件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個是懂得古老的咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠使用拉丁語
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個是像我們這樣擁有強大的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今和天上世界毫無關聯  不受他們的束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且心靈純潔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在地上的人中…那樣的人已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D  O  N  A  B  C
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  小客人醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  普莉姆拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  大家自己談得起勁  我聽得有點無聊就想開始學習了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  說的是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dona  nobis  pacem
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是「給予我們和平」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是拉丁語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰教的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧伽姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧伽姆很厲害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴裡能吐出又大又漂亮的火焰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會把砂糖融化做成漢字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能拼對就能吃掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧伽姆…這種戰爭時刻…你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有如此強大的參謀長在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  能贏  能贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D  O  N  A…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧伽姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  奧伽姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初源之火是生命的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的生命可能會因此燃盡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  這就像是做糖字那樣容易
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  我還不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧伽姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩位…不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在親眼看到世間萬物所追求的理想鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿努文之前絕不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:15:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手  奧伽姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想死嗎  奧伽姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個頑固的老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這裡正是我的戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了開拓今後的道路  我要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我活到現在  就是為了今天這樣的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙由我來對付
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護莉安瓏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧伽姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾德拉姆和墮天之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德拉姆和墮天之翼正在共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人和阿爾撒魯大人都平安無事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我們也加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  但…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是絢麗的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得充滿了幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙在害怕墮天之翼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個了結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好輕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體好輕巧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉比塔斯的力量消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任務才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了  蘇伊露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把復活的大鍋破壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的是妖精族的勇者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在先祖面前抬起頭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好  摩爾嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是有野心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技術和魔法的…精髓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.49,0:19:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  去阿隆那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模仿天上世界建造的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  阿爾撒魯大人也在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人  奧伽姆大人也平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩  奧塔維亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又見面了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那是當然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯蒂  蘇伊露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼  覺得非常的可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂像是要被冰凍一般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  這裡是非常悲傷的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:20:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是王座
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼坐在那裡的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當心點  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰  為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位正是神聖帝國的皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想變老
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.37,0:21:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對生執著的可憐的老人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.15,0:21:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是他最後的下場


